14:39.980 --> 14:41.379
A series of crimes,
actually.

14:41.410 --> 14:43.048
The index fingerprint you found

14:43.080 --> 14:44.206
matches partials
that were found

14:44.250 --> 14:45.649
at the site of 13 murders.

14:45.680 --> 14:47.511
What?!

14:47.550 --> 14:49.518
They happened
in two batches.

14:49.550 --> 14:51.017
Two mass shootings
the DEA thinks

14:51.050 --> 14:52.915
