business for themselves.

14:56.960 --> 14:59.952
In both cases, they believe
the shooter is a Robles assassin

15:00.000 --> 15:01.627
nicknamed "El Mechanico."

15:01.660 --> 15:04.094
Would you get in touch
with the Marchioness?

15:04.130 --> 15:05.392
I would very much like
to ask her

15:05.430 --> 15:06.692
why drug dealers want
to murder her horse.

15:06.730 --> 15:08.960
What else do we know about
this El Mechanico?

15:09.000 --> 15:10.558
BELL:
Not much.

15:10.610 --> 15:13.329
This first massacre happened
at a dock in Tampa.

15:13.380 --> 15:14.608
There was a civilian
cleaning his boat

15:14.640 --> 15:16.676
when the shots started flying.

15:16.710 --> 15:18.143
He gave a description but...

15:18.180 --> 15:20.671
(phone chiming)
no one's seen him since.

15:20.720 --> 15:23.416
Nigella says we can
see her at her hotel.

15:23.450 --> 15:24.610
She's at the Sutner.

15:24.650 --> 15:27.153
Suite 2501.

15:28.760 --> 15:31.320
(distant siren wailing,
car horns honking)

15:50.580 --> 15:53.219
(phone ringing)

15:59.020 --> 16:00.282
Hello?

16:00.320 --> 16:02.311
Nigella, listen
very carefully:

16:02.360 --> 16:04.021
The same man who
killed Dalton Ladd

16:04.060 --> 16:05.084
is targeting you.

16:05.130 --> 16:06.722
NIGELLA:
What?!

16:06.760 --> 16:08.296
Have you noticed
anyone unusual?

16:08.330 --> 16:10.366
Any deliveries
to your room?

16:10.400 --> 16:11.992
No, no, no.

16:12.030 --> 16:13.133
It's been quite peaceful,
actually.

16:13.170 --> 16:14.262
I've just been enjoying
the view.

16:14.300 --> 16:15.733
Your curtains are open?

16:15.770 --> 16:17.465
NIGELLA:
Yeah, just the one.

16:18.810 --> 16:21.370
Would you kindly go into
another room at once?

16:21.410 --> 16:22.707
Why?

16:22.740 --> 16:23.741
(silenced gunshot)

16:28.820 --> 16:30.310
For God sakes, of course

16:30.350 --> 16:32.284
I don't know anybody
in the Robles cartel.

16:32.320 --> 16:35.357
I'm in the peerage.

16:35.390 --> 16:38.689
And I don't understand
why they'd want me dead.

16:38.730 --> 16:40.698
I have no idea whatsoever.

16:40.730 --> 16:42.322
All right, what about
your boyfriend?

16:42.360 --> 16:45.261
You think it's possible he did
business with them and...

16:45.300 --> 16:47.188
hid it from you?
Dalton was an alternate

16:47.240 --> 16:51.131
on the national steeplechase
team in 2000 and 2004.

16:51.170 --> 16:52.637
That's her way of saying no.

16:52.670 --> 16:54.308
What about your
other employees?

16:54.340 --> 16:56.171
She's lying.

16:56.210 --> 16:59.099
I know Miss Mason to be
a woman of low character.

16:59.150 --> 17:00.515
You've incurred
the wrath of these people,

17:00.550 --> 17:02.768
and it wasn't through
an honest difference of opinion.

17:02.820 --> 17:06.381
I will give you access
to all of our books,

17:06.420 --> 17:09.389
records, anything--
but there is no connection

17:09.420 --> 17:12.150
_ between these
Vile people and me.

17:17.230 --> 17:18.162
What's this?

17:18.200 --> 17:20.088
I spent most of the day
as a spare wheel.

17:20.140 --> 17:21.630
I thought I'd make
myself useful.

17:21.670 --> 17:24.537
I know you and Joan rarely
sit down for a meal.

17:24.570 --> 17:26.731
That's by design--
a lingering dinner,

17:26.770 --> 17:28.704
especially in the midst of
a case, is an indulgence.

17:28.740 --> 17:31.277
You think conversation's
an indulgence?

17:31.310 --> 17:32.709
_The meal itself
is an indulgence.

17:32.750 --> 17:34.638
_ Conversation
is an annoyance

17:34.680 --> 17:36.409
within an indulgence...

17:39.750 --> 17:41.354
Well, I suppose
it's harmless enough.

17:41.390 --> 17:43.585
As long as you don't try
to stop me from working.

17:43.630 --> 17:45.120
You're welcome.

17:45.160 --> 17:47.196
So...

17:47.230 --> 17:49.824
did you learn anything?

17:49.860 --> 17:53.364
The police believe a man
named Joaquin Aguilar

17:53.400 --> 17:56.767
heads up the Robles cartel's
East Coast operations.

17:56.800 --> 17:59.405
The cartel is always at odds
with one or another

17:59.440 --> 18:01.601
of its rivals, so the man is
very rarely seen in public.

18:01.640 --> 18:03.540
In fact,
he's only been spotted six times

18:03.580 --> 18:05.707
in the last two years.

18:05.750 --> 18:07.377
He's always at a private box
he maintains

18:07.420 --> 18:09.445
at the Aqueduct
race track.

18:09.480 --> 18:11.516
He's a _horseman.
A pa55ionate one.

18:11.550 --> 18:13.609
There's bad behavior
to be unearthed here.

18:13.660 --> 18:14.684
Be prepared for that.

18:16.490 --> 18:17.650
You seem quite invested

18:17.690 --> 18:19.624
in the idea
that Nigella has changed.

18:19.660 --> 18:22.151
From what I can see,
change is sloppy.

18:22.200 --> 18:23.622
It's a process,
not an absolute state.

18:23.670 --> 18:25.467
Why are you so
invested

18:25.500 --> 18:26.762
in the idea
that Nigella has to be

18:26.800 --> 18:28.336
a good person
to deserve your help?

18:28.370 --> 18:30.361
What are you doing?

18:30.410 --> 18:31.866
Something has just
occurred to me.

18:31.910 --> 18:34.105
Mmm!

18:36.340 --> 18:37.671
This is the best risotto
I have ever had.

18:37.710 --> 18:39.371
(clears throat)

18:39.410 --> 18:41.241
Why are you hiring a chef?
You should do it.

18:41.280 --> 18:44.147
Owning restaurants
is a lot more fun.
Mm.

18:44.190 --> 18:45.646
He means less work.

18:45.690 --> 18:47.715
Yes, I suppose
you could say that.

18:47.760 --> 18:49.682
I don't quite believe

18:49.720 --> 18:51.153
I'm going to say this
to a grown man:

18:51.190 --> 18:52.452
Your food's getting cold.

18:57.730 --> 18:59.220
(phone chimes)

19:02.700 --> 19:04.668
Brilliant.

19:04.710 --> 19:05.768
I've just heard back from
a forensic accountant

19:05.810 --> 19:07.630
I once helped
out of a spot of bother

19:07.680 --> 19:09.830
involving a naked self-portrait
of himself-- anyway--

19:09.880 --> 19:12.508
he's confirmed something
I already suspected.

19:12.550 --> 19:15.269
I noticed that Joaquin Aguilar

19:15.320 --> 19:18.687
comes to the race track when
one of two horses is racmg--

19:18.720 --> 19:21.280
both animals are owned by
Mariotti Farms,

19:21.320 --> 19:24.323
it's a stable and training
facility in New Jersey.

19:24.360 --> 19:26.453
Mariotti Farms,
I've just learned,

19:26.490 --> 19:28.526
received its initial seed money

19:28.560 --> 19:30.266
from a limited liability
corporation

19:30.300 --> 19:31.892
with substantial holdings
in manganese mining

19:31.930 --> 19:33.591
and canned foods.

19:33.640 --> 19:35.198
The corporation has,
three times,

19:35.240 --> 19:37.367
been investigated
by the DEA,

19:37.410 --> 19:40.436
who have long suspected
it is a front for...

19:40.480 --> 19:42.209
the Robles cartel.

19:42.240 --> 19:44.777
You think Joaquin Aguilar

19:44.810 --> 19:46.539
is the real money
behind those horses?

19:46.580 --> 19:47.740
It's called shadow ownership.

19:47.780 --> 19:49.714
Happens all the time
in racing.

19:49.750 --> 19:51.479
Look at this...
(paper rustling)

19:52.950 --> 19:56.556
This is a list of all the horses
owned by Mariotti Farms,

19:56.590 --> 19:57.921
this...

19:57.960 --> 20:00.997
is a list of all Silver Blaze's
sexual partners

20:01.030 --> 20:03.567
since the Marchioness began
pimping him out.

20:03.600 --> 20:05.921
"Twice for No"
is on both these lists.

20:05.970 --> 20:09.360
Joaquin Aguilar paid to have
one of his mares impregnated

20:09.400 --> 20:13.370
by Silver Blaze--
I need Nigella's records.

20:18.850 --> 20:20.977
The pairing alleged to a male
offspring, born healthy,

20:21.020 --> 20:23.887
who was then sold... to...

20:23.920 --> 20:25.785
a third party.

20:25.820 --> 20:27.412
WATSON:
That's weird.

20:27.460 --> 20:29.018
He paid for a champion
to impregnate his horse.

20:29.060 --> 20:30.550
Why would he just
sell off the baby?

20:30.590 --> 20:31.955
HOLMES:
It is curious.

20:31.990 --> 20:34.891
The foal is housed
at a stables in Long Island,

20:34.930 --> 20:36.727
so I say we go and have a look.

20:36.760 --> 20:38.728
But not till_
the morning, right?

20:38.770 --> 20:41.534
So does this mean that
you can actually Sit down

20:41.570 --> 20:42.889
and have some dessert?

20:42.940 --> 20:43.964
Hmm?

20:51.980 --> 20:52.844
Excellent.

20:54.050 --> 20:55.449
(clears throat)

20:56.780 --> 20:57.883
Ah, sorry, I can't do this.

20:57.920 --> 20:59.547
There's just too much tension.

20:59.590 --> 21:01.012
What are you talking about?
There's no tension.

21:01.060 --> 21:02.687
We're having
a nice time.

21:02.720 --> 21:04.358
You must be joking.
Watson carries unease

21:04.390 --> 21:05.823
between her shoulder blades.
Her trape2ius muscles

21:05.860 --> 21:06.986
