My back is fine.

21:08.960 --> 21:11.929
What happened
between you two in London?

21:11.970 --> 21:13.790
(sighs heavily)

21:13.840 --> 21:15.933
I'm not so sure

21:15.970 --> 21:18.063
this is a good idea.

21:18.110 --> 21:19.805
Thank you for
your company.

21:23.910 --> 21:25.798
(door opens, closes)
What is the matter with you?

21:25.850 --> 21:26.839
Your brother is
reaching out to you.

21:26.880 --> 21:28.472
You guys have a chance

21:28.520 --> 21:30.385
to fix things,
and you're wasting it.

21:30.420 --> 21:31.648
I'm not wrong, though.

21:31.690 --> 21:33.089
You're _uncomfortable
in his presence.

21:33.120 --> 21:34.849
I am not uncomfortable
around Mycroft.

21:34.890 --> 21:36.949
I am uncomfortable around you
and Mycroft together.

21:36.990 --> 21:38.548
For what reason?

21:38.590 --> 21:39.784
This is none of your business.

21:39.830 --> 21:40.854
But you're being weird

21:40.900 --> 21:42.629
and I don't
want you to wreck

21:42.660 --> 21:44.093
your relationship with
your brother-- again.

21:44.130 --> 21:46.621
Okay, we had dinner...
I was a little bit nervous

21:46.670 --> 21:48.638
because I thought he was
gonna hit on me,

21:48.670 --> 21:50.900
but it became obvious
that he just wanted
to talk about you.

21:50.940 --> 21:52.908
He was Sincere and sweet

21:52.940 --> 21:54.737
and he's funny, too.
Oh, my God.

21:54.780 --> 21:56.702
I was in London-- I didn't know
he was gonna come here.

21:56.740 --> 21:58.879
You had sex with my brother.

21:58.910 --> 22:00.741
Willingly?

22:00.780 --> 22:02.839
Great-- you had to push,
so now you know.

22:02.880 --> 22:04.586
Two consenting adults
went to bed together.

22:04.620 --> 22:06.042
Okay?
You can let that

22:06.090 --> 22:07.910
ruin your relationship
with your brother, or not.

22:07.960 --> 22:09.951
Your call.

22:18.900 --> 22:21.767
Watson, I've decided not to hold
your dalliance against you.

22:21.800 --> 22:23.506
As you said,
you're a grown woman.

22:25.510 --> 22:26.659
I'm disappointed in you.

22:26.710 --> 22:27.938
I thought you were attempting

22:27.980 --> 22:30.448
to move beyond
petty revenge tactics.

22:30.480 --> 22:32.744
It wasn't revenge.

22:32.780 --> 22:35.647
1-1 have just one question
for the both of you.

22:35.680 --> 22:37.443
Is this going to be
an ongoing arrangement?

22:37.490 --> 22:39.947
Because, if it is,
I'll need to plan accordingly.

22:43.490 --> 22:45.424
You haven't discussed it.

22:45.460 --> 22:47.155
Well, get it sorted
immediately, would you?

22:47.190 --> 22:48.851
It's the least you could do.

22:50.000 --> 22:51.922
Just out of curiosity--
was he any good?

22:51.970 --> 22:53.767
My brother.

22:53.800 --> 22:55.961
Does he have a talent
for the act of coitus?

22:58.710 --> 23:00.029
Mycroft, your thoughts
on Watson?

23:00.070 --> 23:01.537
WOMAN:
We were real surprised

23:01.580 --> 23:03.639
we even got a shot
to bid on a foal

23:03.680 --> 23:05.443
from Silver Blaze
and Twice for No.

23:05.480 --> 23:07.744
This little guy cost us big.

23:07.780 --> 23:10.988
Here he is-- Nutmeg.

23:11.020 --> 23:13.079
You pet him, you got
yourself a friend for life.

23:13.120 --> 23:14.758
Hi, Nutmeg.

23:14.790 --> 23:16.519
You mind
telling me why

23:16.560 --> 23:18.721
the NYPD's so keen
to see a baby horse?

23:18.760 --> 23:20.079
It's a winding tale.

23:20.130 --> 23:21.688
It_ i _nvolves
the British peerage,

23:21.730 --> 23:23.095
syringes full of
concentrated potassium

23:23.130 --> 23:25.894
and 13 drug-related
murders.

23:29.740 --> 23:32.538
WATSON:
You want to tell me what
we're looking at here?

23:32.570 --> 23:34.709
Whorls.
Whirls?

23:34.740 --> 23:36.435
Whorls-- small patches
of hair which grow

23:36.480 --> 23:38.607
in the opposite direction
to the rest of the coat.

23:38.650 --> 23:41.016
I'll only be a moment.

23:41.050 --> 23:42.711
If you can't
wait patiently,

23:42.750 --> 23:45.082
