"I told you so,"

23:50.760 --> 23:52.489
but Nigella Mason
is a horrid witch.

23:52.530 --> 23:54.919
If it gives you no pleasure,
why you looking so satisfied?

23:54.960 --> 23:55.949
Because I know why

23:56.000 --> 23:58.093
Joaquin Aguilar
is angry with her.

23:58.130 --> 24:00.121
Summon the marchioness.

24:00.170 --> 24:01.592
Did you know
there have been

24:01.640 --> 24:03.665
several studies done
on whether or not

24:03.710 --> 24:06.907
the placement of whorls on
horses is a heritable trait?

24:06.940 --> 24:08.669
I beg your pardon?

24:08.710 --> 24:11.804
The placement of those little
cowlicks is inherited.

24:11.850 --> 24:14.068
And why are you
telling me this?

24:14.120 --> 24:16.145
Well, it's not something that
most people would look for,

24:16.180 --> 24:18.011
but appears to be true.

24:18.050 --> 24:19.813
I'll show you.

24:19.850 --> 24:22.557
(Holmes clears throat)

24:22.590 --> 24:24.057
This...
(clears throat)

24:24.090 --> 24:26.229
