between his eyes.

24:30.700 --> 24:33.567
Mmm.
The same is true
of Twice for No,

24:33.600 --> 24:35.864
who recently birthed
Silver Blaze's son.

24:35.900 --> 24:38.164
Now, the laws of nature
tell us that their offspring

24:38.210 --> 24:40.701
should also have whorls
between his eyes.

24:40.740 --> 24:43.129
We looked at this young
beast this morning.

24:43.180 --> 24:48.208
Nutmeg has whorls positioned
well above his eyes.

24:48.250 --> 24:51.686
Which leads me to the
pertinent question:

24:51.720 --> 24:55.258
What exactly happened to
the real Silver Blaze?

24:55.290 --> 24:56.757
Is he dead?

24:56.790 --> 24:58.018
Dead?

24:58.060 --> 24:59.049
(chuckles)

24:59.090 --> 25:01.593
You saw him yourself yesterday.

25:01.630 --> 25:03.097
Well, I saw a horse
that certainly

25:03.130 --> 25:04.825
looked like
Silver Blaze.

25:04.870 --> 25:06.064
But you and I
both know

25:06.100 --> 25:07.965
that the horse
whose sexual favors

25:08.000 --> 25:10.230
you are selling for
upwards of 100,000 a pop

25:10.270 --> 25:12.659
