that I fought

25:21.220 --> 25:23.984
to get ownership of Silver Blaze

25:24.020 --> 25:27.217
included in my prenuptials
with the marquess.

25:27.250 --> 25:29.753
And why shouldn't I
have something to show

25:29.790 --> 25:32.224
for giving years of my life
to that man's lie?

25:32.260 --> 25:35.195
You were married
for 22 months.

25:35.230 --> 25:37.289
Yes, and I
earned that horse

25:37.330 --> 25:38.763
during that stretch--
believe me.

25:38.800 --> 25:40.267
I earned a pack of horses.

25:40.300 --> 25:42.564
And, of course,
it wasn't ten weeks

25:42.600 --> 25:44.136
after we signed
the papers

25:44.170 --> 25:46.559
that I get a call
out of the blue--

25:46.610 --> 25:48.339
3:00 a.m.,
heart failure.

25:48.380 --> 25:52.248
So you hatched a plan to
keep the money rolling in.

25:52.280 --> 25:54.248
Where did you find
the imposter?

25:54.280 --> 25:56.669
Silver Blaze has a brother.

25:56.720 --> 25:58.688
He never amounted to much.

25:58.720 --> 26:01.154
But their markings
are almost identical.

26:01.190 --> 26:03.852
We bought him
for a few hundred quid,

26:03.890 --> 26:05.926
applied a bit of hair dye
here and there.

26:05.960 --> 26:07.951
Dye?
You're charging these people

26:08.000 --> 26:09.854
hundreds of thousands
of dollars.

26:09.900 --> 26:12.164
Don't they want to have proof
that it's the real horse?

26:12.200 --> 26:13.224
Yes. Well,
the racing world's

26:13.270 --> 26:14.760
always been
a little bit backward.

26:14.800 --> 26:16.233
With studding,

26:16.270 --> 26:19.103
most of the scrutiny
falls on the mare.

26:19.140 --> 26:20.129
They're screened
for disease,

26:20.170 --> 26:22.172
for the tendency
to inflict injury

26:22.210 --> 26:23.234
during the live cover.

26:23.280 --> 26:24.838
And the stud, well,

26:24.880 --> 26:27.201
the whole world knew
that Silver Blaze was mine.

26:27.250 --> 26:30.788
There were some requests
for genetic testing.

26:30.820 --> 26:33.311
We took some hair
and some blood

26:33.350 --> 26:35.989
before we got rid
of the body.

26:36.020 --> 26:38.727
So, really, we didn't run
into that many problems.

26:38.760 --> 26:41.888
You're the first three people
who have figured it out.

26:41.930 --> 26:43.227
Actually, we're not.

26:43.260 --> 26:45.626
Joaquin Aguilar
caught on, too.

26:45.670 --> 26:48.059
_But he couldn't
just expose you.

26:48.100 --> 26:51.069
That would destroy the value
of the foal born to his mare.

26:51.110 --> 26:54.170
So he did what drug
kingpins are wont to do.

26:54.210 --> 26:56.872
